videos.description: Brady Manek grabs the rebound and passes to Trae young who knocks down the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Oklahoma's Young on fire early

videos.description: Trae Young gets caught between two defenders then somehow flips the ball to Jamuni McNeace  for the slam.
videos.headline: Young-McNeace connection leads to dunk

videos.description: Trae Young brings the ball up and drains a 3-pointer from way outside.
videos.headline: Oklahoma's Young is a stud

videos.description: Trae Young dribbles down the court in transition and finds Christian James for the alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Sooners' Young-James putting on a show

videos.description: Trae Young comes off the screen and knocks down the corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Sooners' Young is unstoppable

videos.description: Trae Young dribbles then steps back to the 3-pointer, finishing off a 25-point, 10-assist opening 20 minutes.
videos.headline: Sooners' Young caps crazy first half with 3-pointer

videos.description: Trae Young was 6-of-8 from three in the first half scoring 25 points to lead his team.
videos.headline: Sooners' Young scores 25 points in first half

videos.description: Trae Young says he enjoyed getting his teammates involved more than anything.
videos.headline: Sooners' Young big night leads team to win
